OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FMostly cloudy with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain slowly transferring north-
OL,7,Feastwards through the day. Some
OL,8,Fbrighter intervals may develop for a
OL,9,Ftime, which could trigger a few
OL,10,Fafternoon showers or thunderstorms.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,13,FIncreasingly cloudy and breezy on
OL,14,FSunday, with patchy light rain late.
OL,15,FBand of rain moving east on Monday.
OL,16,FCooler and windy on Tuesday, with
OL,17,Fsunny spells and showers, occasionally
OL,18,Fheavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
